snippet.title: 【SHUNYA】Steam game page trailer
snippet.description:
SHUNYA
Platform : PC Steam
Hello everyone, "SHUNYA" is a 2D platform puzzle game with a Cube drawing mechanism. Now it finally has a Steam page. If you like it, please add it to your wishlist and share it to your friend.

Wishlist Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2587210/SHUNYA/
Thank you ~
